Package: sppt.aggregated.data
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Pattern Point Test for Aggregated Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Martin", "Andresen", email = "martin.andresen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Contributor", "Name", role = "ctb"))
Description: Performs spatial pattern point tests on aggregated count data using 
    bootstrap resampling. Compares spatial distributions between variables and 
    calculates S-Index metrics to quantify spatial pattern overlap. Supports 
    visualization and export of results in multiple formats.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports:
    Matrix,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    rlang,
    sf,
    stats
Suggests:
    knitr (>= 1.40),
    rmarkdown (>= 2.20),
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/martin-a-andresen/sppt.aggregated.data
